<div class="ufonews" style="margin-bottom:1em;">
<h2 class="title"> <span class="mw-headline" id="Next_licensing_step">Next licensing step</span></h2>
<div class="content">
<p>Our final goal for the licensing was reached today. We are now fully Debian compliant. This is true for both 2.6-dev and <a href="/wiki/Changelog/2.5" title="Changelog/2.5">2.5</a>. You can find the list of licenses <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://ufoai.org/licenses/">here</a>.
</p><p>We can now finally prepare the 2.5 release and we really hope that we are a part of the Debian world from that release on. We would reach a lot more users with that and hopefully would also get some new contributors.
</p><p>Stay tuned for the monthly that is hopefully going to be posted soon.
</p>
</div>
<div class="meta" style="font-size:80%; text-align:right;"><span class="date">2014-06-01</span> — <span class="author"><a href="/wiki/User:Mattn" title="User:Mattn">mattn</a></span></div>
